rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0001
rows.name:
What's wrong?
Is something troubling you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0002
rows.name: Try talking to Tatsu, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0003
rows.name: Kyaaa[ST:wide ]â€• Aliens, yo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0004
rows.name:
And they've got Nopon takeout,
bringing him along like a packed lunch, eh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0005
rows.name:
How rude, meh!
Tatsu is not a packed lunch, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0006
rows.name: These Earthlings are Tatsu's assistants, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0007
rows.name: Assistants?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0008
rows.name: Er, no! Assis... Assisting... FRIENDS, meh!

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Friends?
Then that species isn't related to Growth, no?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0010
rows.name: Sorry to startle you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0011
rows.name:
We are Earthlings.
Currently we are in a hostile relationship with Growth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0012
rows.name:
Hostile towards Growth?
Then it seems like you'll become our allies, jan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0013
rows.name: We are Ma-non people, yo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0014
rows.name:
As you can see, because we possess culture and high intelligence,
we're targeted by Growth, yo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0015
rows.name:
You guys will help us, right?!
I'm sure of it, right?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0016
rows.name: Right. If there's anything we can do to help...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0017
rows.name:
You can, you can, yo!
You guys are our saviors, yo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0018
rows.name: This is where we are now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0019
rows.name:
At the bottom of the fog in this crevasse,
there's a spaceship, y'know![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0022
rows.name:
But, targeted by Growth's anti-aircraft weapons,
we can't move![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0023
rows.name:
So if we destroy those anti-air weapons,
your spaceship can take off, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0024
rows.name:
Yes, yo! Growth's anti-air weapons
are installed at these three locations![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0025
rows.name: Please destroy them all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0026
rows.name:
Understood. We're not happy about
them controlling the airspace either.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0027
rows.name: We'd like to eliminate them quickly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs05060100_MSG0028
rows.name:
You'll do it!?
You guys are kind![ST:wait ]
